---
title: Apricot and Mustard-Glazed Ham with Mashed Potatoes and Roasted Veggie Sticks
description: The combination of apricot jam and mustard makes a surprisingly delicious glaze for ham steaks! If you happen to have some buns at home, leftovers make a great ham sandwich!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/apricot-and-mustard-glazed-ham-003585bf.jpg
